### Step 1: Login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "superadmin@rim.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Step 2: Copy token แล้ว update @token
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOjIsImVtYWlsIjoic3VwZXJhZG1pbkByaW0uY29tIiwicm9sZSI6IlNVUEVSX0FETUlOIiwiaWF0IjoxNzY2MTUxODg4LCJleHAiOjE3NjY3NTY2ODh9.I4mLQTempkvb__L8Y2Tsf5OYVVwBQkyA_t5ThmG8T8Y

### Step 3: Test Get All Stores
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stores
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Step 4: Test with Pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stores?page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Step 5: Test with Filters
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stores?status=ACTIVE&province=Bangkok
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Step 6: Test with Search
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stores?search=Watsons
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Step 7: Test Get Store by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stores/10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Step 8: Test Get Statistics
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stores/7/statistics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Step 9: Test Create Store
POST http://localhost:3000/api/stores
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "storeCode": "TEST-999",
  "name": "Test Store",
  "company": "Test Company",
  "province": "Bangkok",
  "storeType": "PERMANENT",
  "storeStatus": "ACTIVE"
}

### Step 10: Test Update Store
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/stores/7
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "02-999-8888",
  "email": "updated@test.com"
}

### Step 11: Test Soft Delete (ใช้ PATCH แทน DELETE)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/stores/7
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "storeStatus": "INACTIVE"
}

### Step 12: Download Template (ใช้ Browser)
# เปิด browser: http://localhost:3000/api/stores/template

### Step 13: Export Stores (ใช้ Browser)
# เปิด browser: http://localhost:3000/api/stores/export?status=ACTIVE